model

Class MusicCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.MusicCollection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CassetteCollection, CDCollection, VinylCollection

    public class MusicCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    MusicCollection is a parent class to Cassette, CD, and Vinyl. It holds variables that each one of these classes have in common. Artist: The artist of this music collectible. Year: The year this music collectible was released. Album: The album name of this music collectible. Run Time: The length of the music collectible with respect to time.
    Author:
    Travis Lawson
